# ğŸŒ Hosting a Website using Terraform and AWS S3

This guide explains how to host a simple static website on AWS S3 using Terraform â€” a perfect starting point for DevOps beginners!

---

## ğŸ§¾ Prerequisites

- AWS Account
- Terraform installed
- AWS CLI installed and configured (`aws configure`)
- A simple `index.html` file

---

## ğŸ“ Project Structure

project-folder/
